description.narrative: Assist the Government of Liberia (GoL) to resolve impediments to effective implementation of its anti-money laundering and countering the financing of terrorism (AML/CFT) regime. Capacity building activities are focused, in particular, on improving the operation of the financial intelligence unit (FIU); financial sector supervision, with an initial emphasis on the banking sector; and financial crimes case development, including inter-agency collaboration on analysis, investigation, and prosecution of predicate crimes and associated money laundering.
